Text: "Can I take a photo?\u201D, I asked the street beach vendor.\n\n\u201CHow much\
  \ do you pay me?\u201C, he responded, smiling friendly, his white teeth showing.\n\
  \n\u201CI buy a cold water from you, ok?\u201D \u2013 \u201Cok!\u201D\n\n\n\nWe\
  \ hiked down the rocky trail to Nyang-Nyang Beach, near Uluwatu in South Bali. Only\
  \ experienced surfer come here to enjoy the thrill of a wave ride.\n\n\nReport this\
  \ ad\n \nHere, at the beach Since a couple of years now, he comes to the beach to\
  \ sell cold drinks and snacks. The surfers trust him, leaving their belongings with\
  \ him while catching waves"
